fb
fgAdds a user to your Friends List.

Users who are on your friends list can send you eXpress messages even when
you have eXpress messages disabled.

You can also be notified with a short message when users on your Friends 
List log on and off the BBS.

You can also add Remote users to your friends list with this syntax:

    username@BBS

